9/23/97 - Motown Cafe - World Hunger Year CD Release show of "One Step Up/Two Steps Back: The Songs of Bruce Springsteen". I was the Musical Director for the night and JD&SC acted as the house band at times during the night which included The Smithereens, Southside Johnny, Max Weinberg, Richie Havens and other great artists.
